Package parser.nodes.methods

This package contains classes that are used to deal with method calls. It has a class that deals with calls to the underlying program (MazeActionNode). It also has a class that deal with calls to methods on user created variables (MethodNode). Finally, it also has a class that is used to validate each method (including MazeActionNode). it check the number and type of the parameters supplied to each method.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    MazeActionNode
    This class deals with calls to maze actions
    MethodNode
    Class that handles the execution of methods
    MethodValidator
    Class used to validate the number of arguments and their types.
